5. Create a polymorphic function that works with different shapes
class Circle:
    def draw(self):
        print("Drawing Circle")

class Rectangle:
    def draw(self):
        print("Drawing Rectangle")

def display(shape):
    shape.draw()

c = Circle()
r = Rectangle()

display(c)
display(r)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. Create a Bank system with SavingsAccount and CurrentAccount
